Program: Omnibus
Title: The King's Films
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376mg2
Last Broadcast Date: 29 July 2002
'The whole country became a kind of musical comedy'. King Norodom Sihanouk of Cambodia produced a total of 50 films between 1966 and 2006. A look at what the films he made reveal about his style of leadership.